BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:lSlwI-X9t-6Nv1VXJVtFK
SUMMARY:Behind the Seams: Roaring '20s
DTSTAMP:20260327T031541Z
DTSTART:20260516T110000Z
DESCRIPTION:Behind the Seams is back\\\, with a closer look at the artifact
	s than ever before! One hundred years later\\\, women’s fashions of the 19
	20s continue to shock and to dazzle. Hemlines rose up to the knee and even
	ingwear were built to move\\\, shake\\\, and sparkle. Join Curator of Coll
	ections\\\, Clara Berg for a historical overview and then an intimate view
	ing of the most stunning 1920s dresses from the museum collection. \\nA me
	mber pre-sale for this event will begin on March 11 and run until March 23
	. Secure your spot early by becoming a MOHAI member today! \\nFor accessib
	ility support\\\, contact programs@mohai.org two weeks before the program.
	\n\nhttps://mohai.org/event/behind-the-seams-roaring-20s/\n\nFrom MOHAI - 
	Museum of History & Industry
URL:https://mohai.org/event/behind-the-seams-roaring-20s/
LOCATION:Norcliffe Conference Room\\\, MOHAI 860 Terry Ave N\\\, Seattle\\\
	, WA\\\, 98109\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:mohai
CATEGORIES:MOHAI - Museum of History & Industry
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
